  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Clan</p><p>Prerequisite: Genwa Clan, Level 12+</p><hr /><p>The power and influence of technology continue to grow as the world continues to evolve. You are a part of this trend, exceeding all those around you who have become dated. You gain the following benefits;</p><ul><li><p>You gain access to another Data Channel.</p></li><li><p>You can perform a Data Leak a number of times equal to your Intelligence modifier, instead of only twice</p></li><li><p>When you would use Stable Frequency to change the duration of a jutsu to 1 minute, you no longer have to double the jutsu's cost to do so. If you still do, the duration becomes 3 minutes.</p></li><li><p>You cannot lose concentration of Genwa Hijutsu as the result of taking damage or failing a concentration check.</p></li></ul>",
